import ListOfElements from '../../components/ListOfElements' import Button from '../../components/Button' import { useHandleClickAll } from '../../hooks/handleClickAll' import { useLocation } from 'wouter' export default async function SearchAll({ params }) { const keyword = params const [,pushLocation] = useLocation() const {handleClick, parameter} = useHandleClickAll(keyword) return parameter === "False" ? pushLocation('/404') : await
}
